description:
NatNet's client/server architecture allows client applications to run on the same network or computer as the tracking software (Motive). The SDK integrates seamlessly with standard languages (C/C++/C#

Please refer to the NatNet API USer's Guide for more information.
https://docs.optitrack.com/developer-tools/natnet-sdk/natnet-4.0#natnet-sdk

A list of changes made in each version can be found at the following website:
https://www.optitrack.com/support/downloads/developer-tools.html
title: NatNet SDK
